com.pb.sawdust.calculator

Class NumericFunctionN

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pb.sawdust.calculator.NumericFunctionN
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NumericFunction0, NumericFunction1, NumericFunction2, NumericFunctionN.FlexFunctionN, PartialNumericFunctionN, SimpleCollapsibleFunction

    public abstract class NumericFunctionN
extends java.lang.Object
    The NumericFunctionN abstract class is used to specify functions which take one or more numbers as an argument and return a number.
